            <div id="resilient-coders" class="logo card targetable">Resilient Coders</div>
            <div id="velir" class="logo card targetable">Velir</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="testimonials">
        <div class="container">
          <header class="section--header">
            <h1 class="text-heading-one">Testimonials</h1>
          </header>
          <figure class="quote">
            <blockquote><p>I have worked with multiple developers from East Coast Product on a variety of projects. In each instance, even though they were remote, the ECP developers have made it a point to become a fully integrated part of the team. They communicate effectively, meet deadlines, and most importantly, produce high-quality deliverables. I would recommend working with East Coast Product to any of my colleagues and look forward to my next experience working with them myself.</p></blockquote>
            <figcaption>
              <p>Kyle Cedrone,<br />Lead Project Manager at <a href="https://www.velir.com/">Velir</a></p>
            </figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure class="quote">
            <blockquote><p>East Coast Productâ€™s Agile approach allowed for close collaboration and for both teams to iterate on the product quickly. They excel at UX and keeping the end user in mind, and were strong communicators at the price of offshore resources. They proved highly adaptable, proactive, and valuable.</p></blockquote>
            <figcaption>
              <p>Chris Bunk,<br />COO at <a href="http://www.hcsafety.com/">Human Condition Safety</a></p>
            </figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure class="quote">
            <blockquote><p>The assets built by East Coast Product were acquired by another company. The client most appreciated the combination of project management, transparency, accountability, and quality of code. They executed everything that was asked for in a forward-thinking technical way.</p></blockquote>
            <figcaption>
              <p>Dave McLaughlin,<br />CEO & Founder at <a href="https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/vsnap">Vsnap</a></p>
            </figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="mentions">
        <div class="container">
          <header class="section--header">
            <h1 class="text-heading-one">Media mentions</h1>
          </header>
          <div class="mentions-list">
            <% collections.mentions.forEach(function(mention){ %>
            <a href="<%= mention.mentionURL %>" class="mention card">
              <div class="mention-logo-wrap">
                <img src="/images/mention-logos/<%= mention.publicationLogo %>" alt="Logo of <%= mention.publication %>" class="mention-logo" />
              </div>
              <h2 class="text-heading-two mention-title">
                <span class="link-surrogate"><%= mention.mentionTitle %></h2></span>
              <h3 class="paragraph--minor mention-date"><%= mention.publication %> | <%= mention.mentionDate %></h3>
            </a><!-- end of .card -->
            <% }) %>
          </div><!-- end of .mentions-list -->
        </div>
      </section>

    </main>
    <% include partials/footer %>
  </body>
</html>
